{"tid":721343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FAKE NEWS: 北韓「升級核設施」根本同Trump嘅「北韓棄核」無關","createTime":"2018-06-28T15:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T08:03:30.000Z","uid":131691,"like":87,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"0f5c5b9d591ca67ea37398b7fcb132347e039a69","tid":721343,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T15:56:47.000Z","msg":"估唔到連登仔連CNN呢啲黨媒都信... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識睇梗係睇root source: 38north，係佢提供衛星圖片同埋原本個report：<a href=\"https://www.38north.org/2018/06/yongbyon062618/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.38north.org%2F2018%2F06%2Fyongbyon062618%2F&d=RYqZaRrScIHxWGlkNoPyFZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=635a08b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.38north.org/2018/06/yongbyon062618/</a><br />\n<br />\n我quote佢個summary最後一段：<br />\nContinued work at the Yongbyon facility should not be seen as having any relationship to North Korea&rsquo;s pledge to denuclearize. The North&rsquo;s nuclear cadre can be expected to proceed with business as usual until specific orders are issued from Pyongyang.<br />\n<br />\n細節：個report比較嘅係二三月同埋六月廿一號，所以任何改變根本同啱啱先傾掂嘅棄核協議無關，根本唔係CCN呀，WSJ呀想營造出嚟嘅「Trump一傾完棄核，北韓就即刻起多啲核武！」fake news假像。<br />\n<br />\n再睇多啲，多咗嘅只不過係一個三月已經起緊嘅水塔，係廿一號好似起完咁話。<br />\n<br />\n連登仔睇新聞唔該用下腦，有陣時歐美嘅fake news同中國嘅fake news有得fight。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/235557_2b7f9ad54ceeb02f5a6f15f06e3dcfc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F235557_2b7f9ad54ceeb02f5a6f15f06e3dcfc8.jpg&h=dd1e51a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/235355_6707eaa909b66a885eb68416faf3ebae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F235355_6707eaa909b66a885eb68416faf3ebae.png&h=de562b22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/235626_b24ae085c0d441690016c343e2bb176f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F235626_b24ae085c0d441690016c343e2bb176f.jpg&h=2674c44d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b00b45aa0d791679f923504c160382b2ac97adb6","tid":721343,"uid":131691,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:13:53.000Z","msg":"無人應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b9aad4ee7a444248132c7c0058d5e783f890d8","tid":721343,"uid":78716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8121ea8ea7687ec8a4c4cb4e26b612245c8acf","tid":721343,"uid":64191,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:19:15.000Z","msg":"又要召喚you are fake news"},{"pid":"ae43351338171eb7d22cfbb247de52d951056f65","tid":721343,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:21:58.000Z","msg":"技術性擊倒"},{"pid":"736a8defcf02b5d9f84b5fe39c6e597726488222","tid":721343,"uid":131691,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"東亞嘅fake news係邊個寫？嚟自北方嘅中國蝗蟲。<br />\n<br />\n歐美嘅fake news係邊個寫？嚟自沙漠嘅猶太蝗蟲。<br />\n<br />\n兩個民族都係最叻話人哋嘅功勞係佢自己，人哋嘅金錢係佢自己，人哋嘅土地係佢自己。<br />\n<br />\n係人類歷史上嘅寄生蟲。"},{"pid":"e81c2033549829c385dbcbc7d865da9862268329","tid":721343,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:24:17.000Z","msg":"Fake news"},{"pid":"2906cf6791b1049d2d670e9ff840e03fd0359fe8","tid":721343,"uid":83623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:28:29.000Z","msg":"Especially at the Experimental Light Water Reactor (ELWR), where the new engineering office building appears externally complete and a small building similar to the one observed at the Radiochemical Laboratory has been erected.<br />\n個到同時起埋工程